<br>
*go to a zone with Undead (that dont run) or a place like Sarnak fort where mobs dont run until they are the last of their kind alive.<br>
<br>
*Uber Buff the PLevelee.<br>
<br>
*DS everyone (including Plevelers).<br>
<br>
*Have PLevelee run through zone pulling (4 times the amount of people involved) making sure to do some damage on each mob.<br>
<br>
*PLevelee returns to Plevelers who are sittin (and KOS).<br>
<br>
*The mobs will spread themselves out amongst each person there...4 each.<br>
<br>
*Let the thorns do the work, and finish off the last few runners.<br>
<br>
This is the same as a regular Plevel session, except it gives exp faster based on how many people are involved.<br>
<br>
It sounds ridiculous, but I did a mini version of it last nite killing 8 mobs at once and only using 20m.  Wouldnt it be neat if we found a place and tried it killing 12 or 16 mobs at a time? hehe<br>
<br>
Just a random thought shoot down at will.<br>
<br>
Neg sides:<br>
<br>
*alot of trouble for a lil exp.<br>
*good luck finding a zone where U can pull 16 mobs on prexus.  (MM *cough*)<br>
<br>
But it should be done just for the record heh.<br>
<br>
